getAndUploadHash(File) - Static method in class me.voidxwalker.serversiderng.ServerSideRNG
Packs the current world folder and the latest.log file into a ZIP file named "verification-[worldFileName].zip" in the ServerSideRNG.verificationFolder using IOUtils.packZipFile(String, String, String) It then converts the ZIP-File into a Hash using IOUtils.zipToHash(File) and sends it to the Verification-Server using ServerSideRNG.uploadHashToken(long, String) This method should be called asynchronously via ServerSideRNG.uploadHash(boolean, boolean) if possible.
